What is the projected market size & growth rate of the Learning Analytics Solution Market?

Market Analysis and Insights :

Global Learning Analytics Solution Market

Learning analytics solution market will reach at an estimated value of USD 13.2 billion by 2028 and grow at a CAGR of 21.45% in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028. Rise in the need for data-driven decisions to improve education quality is an essential factor driving the learning analytics solution market.

Education and learning analytics is defined as a measurement, collection, analysis and reporting regarding learners and their contexts so as to optimize learning and understand the environment in which it occurs. This technique help teacher to progress their student’s knowledge and skills and also provides helpful help for both students and educators.

Rise in the technological investments among education institutes is a crucial factor accelerating the market growth, also rise in the need for data-driven decisions to improve education quality, rise in the use of e-learning and mobile learning and rise in the awareness regarding the potential of learning analytics in enhancing or changing a learning system are the major factors among others boosting the learning analytics solution market. Moreover, rise in cloud-based learning analytics solutions and rise in the advent of machine learning and artificial intelligence will further create new opportunities for learning analytics solution market in the forecast period mentioned above.

However, lack of awareness and skilled resources to manage education analytics solutions are the major factors among others restraining the market growth, and will further challenge the learning analytics solution market in the forecast period mentioned above.

